assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Wetown Electric Group Co., Ltd. engages in the research, development, production, and sale of electrical products in China, South-East Asia, Australia, South America, Africa, and internationally. It offers low and high voltage, wind and nuclear power, and data center busway products, as well as other related products; and electrical equipment products, including high and low voltage switchgear, box-type substation, distribution boxes, column head cabinet, intelligent medium-voltage circuit breakers, and others. The company offers copper and aluminum raw materials for bus bar manufacturing and related industries, as well as tin-coated ribbon used in photovoltaic solar module industry; new material products, including rail transit embedded channel, pipe gallery support, anti-seismic support suspension, photovoltaic support, and others; cable tray products, such as steel, aluminum alloy, and data center cable trays, as well as other related products; and mesh trays, optical fiber channels, wiring frames, wire fixers, and other products. It serves government building, financial real estate, wind power, petrochemicals, ferrous metallurgy, ship, city hotel, machine, power, car manufacturer, tobacco, paper, hospital, IT, data center, communications, food, transportation, clothing textile, and photovoltaic industries. The company was founded in 1986 and is based in Yangzhong, China.
